    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2149120/extras/42fe20ef8793e785e725b15f163a6143.poster.avif?t=1721387478\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2149120/extras/42fe20ef8793e785e725b15f163a6143.webm?t=1721387478\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2149120/extras/42fe20ef8793e785e725b15f163a6143.mp4?t=1721387478\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>探索莫皮罗小岛，发现深海的秘密！</strong></h2><br>开启热带小岛莫皮罗之旅吧！开启海洋之旅，发现小岛周边的秘密！  与海豚朋友基努一同潜入充满生机与色彩的深海。了解海洋生物和生态，同时帮助当地环保主义者拯救岛屿于灾难。<br><br>你在莫皮罗小岛上的假期可不会轻松！不过还好，任务途中，祖父和小岛居民会向你伸出援手。了解这个岛屿的民间传说和传统，拯救岛屿于灾难。踏上奇妙的冒险，沉浸在先祖的遗产中，解开魔法图腾的秘密。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2149120/extras/32eb898a6b8ee77f8fe3ae30984f0358.poster.avif?t=1721387478\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2149120/extras/32eb898a6b8ee77f8fe3ae30984f0358.webm?t=1721387478\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2149120/extras/32eb898a6b8ee77f8fe3ae30984f0358.mp4?t=1721387478\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>和伙伴海豚基努一起发现水下世界隐藏的宝藏。参加当地人的保护任务，为岛上的野生动物拍照，完成你的百科。 <br><br>领略海洋丰富的生态系统并学习如何保护它。用你的力量去帮助濒临灭绝的海洋生物。<br><br>是一款带有奇幻色彩的教育冒险游戏，背景设定在美丽的热带岛屿莫皮罗。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2149120/extras/57778a7ca514d4063a67f918a40c87cb.poster.avif?t=1721387478\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2149120/extras/57778a7ca514d4063a67f918a40c87cb.webm?t=1721387478\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2149120/extras/57778a7ca514d4063a67f918a40c87cb.mp4?t=1721387478\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>特点 </strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>充满神秘和魔法的原创故事<br></li><li>了解生态学的有趣方法，其中的信息都经过仔细查阅<br></li><li>海洋物种的百科全书<br></li><li>优美又原始的风景供你探索 </li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2149120/extras/850acd9a56de25bae8c5fbc34afb9206.poster.avif?t=1721387478\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2149120/extras/850acd9a56de25bae8c5fbc34afb9206.webm?t=1721387478\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2149120/extras/850acd9a56de25bae8c5fbc34afb9206.mp4?t=1721387478\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
